Software:
TRF + RepeatMaker + RepeatModeler + RepeatProteinMask + LTR_finder (cdhit, repeatclassifier, repeatmasker)

Cmd TRF: 
	• trf /scratch/project_2006483/Dan_Compare/00.genome/PpunV8.fa 2 5 7 80 10 50 2000 -d -h
	• Perl ConvertTrf2Gff.pl PpunV8.fa.2.5.7.80.10.50.2000.dat PpunV8.fix.trf.gff
	Slurm parameter: 1 thread 10G memory -> ~700 Mb genome; run ~1.5h

Cmd RepeatMasker:
	• RepeatMasker -species Actinopteri -nolow -norna -no_is -gff PpunV8.fa -pa 40
Notes: 
*RepeatMasker needs lots of memory exceed >150G; should be given 40 threads incase tooooo slow. Before running, need change to conda env "repeatmasker"
*Different species/taxa used in Repeatmasker will influence the total gene, "-species Actinopteri" used for 9-spined. 

Cmd RepeatModeler:
	• BuildDatabase -name Ppun PpunV8.fa 2>&1 | tee 01.BuildDatabase.log;
	• RepeatModeler -threads 20 -database Ppun -engine ncbi
	• RepeatMasker -lib ./RM_207463.MonNov211407572022/consensi.fa.classified -pa 60 PpunV8.fa
Notes:
	• repeatmodeler要跑2-3天，sbatch任务要留够时间
	• '-pa' should change to '-threads' after repeatmodeler updated.


Cmd LTR_Finder:
Work path: /scratch/project_2006483/Dan_Compare/03.annot/01.repeat/05.LTR_finder
	• ltr_finder ./splitBYscaff/LG17/LG17.fa -s /projappl/project_2006483/LTR_Finder/source/tRNA/eukaryotic-tRNAs.fa -w 2 > ./ltr_finder_out/LG17.out
Notes:
*LTR_Finder do not have parallel module, it will be very slow if do not split the fasta before.

(cdhit之后，repeatclassifier贼爱中断，要确认是否每一条都跑完了）

